<% if  @dinosaurs_not_fed != 0 %>
<h1>Keep Going!</h1>
<h3>Dinosaurs are hungry!</h3>
<% else %>
<h3>Great Job! Keep up the Good Work!</h3>
<% end %>


Number of Dinosaurs in Park: <%= @number_of_dinosaurs %><br>
How many times dinosaurs fed today: <%= @dinosaurs_fed_today %><br>
_________________________________________________________<br>
